      %h2 Browse apps

      %p Most people will access mstdn.social directly with the web browser, however if you prefer you can use mstdn.social with any of these apps!

      %h3 Apple iOS

      %p
        = link_to 'Amaroq', 'https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/amarok-for-mastodon/id1214116200?ls=1&mt=8'
         (recommended) - a free and lightweight universal client for any Mastodon instance! Simply enter the instance you belong to, log in, and enjoy the all the wonders of the federated social network from your phone.
      %p
        = link_to 'Mast', 'https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/mast/id1437429129?mt=8'
         - a free app built with iOS design guidelines in mind. Itâ€™s as feature-packed as it is gorgeous. With customisable content and themes.
      %p
