         - a paid client for the Mastodon social network. It is beautiful, and full of character and whimsy.

      %h3 Google Android

      %p
        = link_to 'Tusky (free)', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.keylesspalace.tusky'
         (recommended) - a free lightweight client - It supports all features, like photos, videos, lists, custom emojis and is designed according to material guidelines.

      %p
        = link_to 'SubwayTooter (free)', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.juggler.subwaytooter'
